public static Collection subtractByID(Collection a, Collection b) { Collection retColl = new ArrayList(); PersistentObject po = null; Iterator it = a.iterator(); while (it.hasNext()) { po = (PersistentObject) it.next(); if (findFirstByID(b, po.getId()) == null) { retColl.add(po); } } return retColl; }
